---
const imageUrl = '/images/nomad-mag-google.webp'
---

<section class="py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-16 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div animate-fade-in-up class="order-1 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src={imageUrl}
          decoding="async"
          class="w-[300px] -rotate-5 md:w-[500px]"
          alt="Woman with binoculars looking out over a road, representing the growing digital nomad community"
        />
      </div>
      <div animate-fade-in-up class="order-2 space-y-6 text-center opacity-0 md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-5xl leading-tight font-bold lg:text-6xl">Growing Digital Nomad Community</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400">
          Just a decade ago, even the notion of aspiring to become a <a href="/blog/what-is-the-definition-of-a-digital-nomad" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">digital nomad</a> was bizarre, and we, the pioneers of digital nomadism, were a rare breed, huddled in the confines of <a href="/blog/coworking-vs-cafes-best-workspaces-for-digital-nomads" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">co-working spaces</a>. Today, we roam the globe proudly, constantly growing our community with millions of digital nomads around the world! If you've chosen to embrace living as a nomad, you'll find a home wherever you plant your laptop.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <p class="text-base text-neutral-400">
            Learn more about <a href="/blog/nomad-list-the-oldest-go-to-resource-for-discovering-the-best-cities-for-remote-work" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">finding the perfect nomad destination</a> or connect with fellow nomads through our <a href="/nomad_directory" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">community directory</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
